---
// ProblemSection - The Gym Owner's Dilemma: 3 pain point cards
---

<section class="problem-section noise-bg">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>
        The Gym Owner's <span class="dim">Dilemma</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        You opened your gym or studio to build freedom. Instead, you built a 70-hour-a-week job with no end in sight.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap icon-red">
          <iconify-icon icon="lucide:alert-triangle" class="card-icon"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3>The Anxiety Cycle</h3>
        <p>
          Every month starts at zero. You don't know if you'll make rent, pay yourself, or keep the lights on. The mental toll is crushing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap icon-orange">
          <iconify-icon icon="lucide:clock" class="card-icon"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3>Time Poverty</h3>
        <p>
          60-70 hour weeks. Running classes, managing schedules, handling admin, trying to "figure out marketing." No time for family. No time for yourself.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap icon-yellow">
          <iconify-icon icon="lucide:help-circle" class="card-icon"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3>The Doubt</h3>
        <p>
          Was opening this studio a mistake? Your family questions it. You question it. Every "guru" promises magic but delivers nothing.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--page-bg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .problem-section { padding: 8rem 0; }
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .container { padding: 0 2rem; }
  }

  .section-header {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display, 'Clash Grotesk', sans-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .dim { color: var(--text-dim); }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }

  .pain-card {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .pain-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-hover-border);
  }

  .icon-wrap {
    width: 3rem; height: 3rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .icon-red { background: var(--red-icon-bg); }
  .icon-red .card-icon { color: var(--red-icon-text); font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .icon-orange { background: var(--orange-icon-bg); }
  .icon-orange .card-icon { color: var(--orange-icon-text); font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .icon-yellow { background: var(--yellow-icon-bg); }
  .icon-yellow .card-icon { color: var(--yellow-icon-text); font-size: 1.5rem; }

  .pain-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display, 'Clash Grotesk', sans-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .pain-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
